ets/faces/husky/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">下流賤格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一味靠嚇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></strong></span></blockquote><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"aa0713da20d2a50b422bd1f43886277f6baed8a0","tid":1442004,"uid":142433,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:02:03.000Z","msg":"好多連登仔對字眼既詮譯總係有少許偏差<br />\nBe water 就解做完全散水 返屋企<br />\nHit and run 就係得run 但唔會hit<br />\n<br />\n你要消耗敵人體力同分散兵力 所以先會run<br />\n但敵人未到未部署你就run 你只係玩緊出左黎既手足<br />\n而家就係擺幾隻鬼 引導大家去某幾個地方<br />\n或者淨係收風大家會去邊快閃 對方根本唔需要調兵<br />\n<br />\n總結就係 be water 又好 hit and run 又好<br />\n首先要明白左套戰術既真正意義 之後嚴格執行<br />\n否則 會玩死埋自己"},{"pid":"f93022424856625d6002be172db3b8ac56dcb005","tid":1442004,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:07:36.000Z","msg":"<code>push</code>"},{"pid":"5bfd98a8256ddf8c4329af379ecd69f1ccfda96a","tid":1442004,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:07:50.000Z","msg":"<code>push</code>"},{"pid":"8f32a1756006c24878fa0b9b69b024a14230df07","tid":1442004,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim